articles.author: Ronald Quinlan
articles.title: Citigroup signs deal for new European HQ in Dublin docklands - The Irish Times
articles.description: Global banking giant strikes agreement with Johnny Ronan’s RGRE for 300,000sq ft office campus at Waterfront South Central
articles.content:
Citigroup has signed for a new headquarters in Dublin, in a boost for the office market in the capital.
